Package universitysystem.entity

Class Manager

java.lang.Object
universitysystem.entity.User
universitysystem.entity.Employee
universitysystem.entity.Manager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<User>, CanCreate, CanLogin, Runnable, StudentsInfo, Subscription, TeachersInfo
public class Manager extends Employee implements TeachersInfo, StudentsInfo, Serializable
Represents a Manager within the university system. A manager is an employee who handles administrative tasks such as processing registration requests, managing courses, and coordinating the university system.
